
'''= Sharitories is a global project with a very practical scope: to create a Collaborative Territories Toolkit for local policy-makers around the world who wish to implement collaborative or sharing initiatives in their local areas and help them thrive.'''

URL = http://www.sharitories.net/


=Description=

"Sharitories is born from OuiShare, a global community and think and do-tank with the mission to build and nurture a collaborative society by connecting people, organizations and ideas around fairness, openness and trust.

The Collaborative Territories Toolkit will be based on contributions and best practices from across the globe, collected from thought leaders and practitioners who work to speed up the transition towards a collaborative society."


=Status=

"This initiative was born thanks to the support of our main founding partner Forum PA: the first draft of the Collaborative Territories Toolkit will be presented and elaborated during a workshop organised during the Smart City Exhibition in Bologna, held between 22-24 October 2014, a conference organised by Forum PA and other partners."

